function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorDetector) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActorDetector) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_BANTER, idActorDetector)
	end
	
end

function Start()
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.25)
	
	bNPCSpoke = false
	
	
T_MONSTERS = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "MONSTERS")

	-- Awaken
	for i, idMonster in ipairs(T_MONSTERS) do
		-- Hydra.TraceScreen(idMonster)
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMonster) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idMonster) then
		
			-- Hydra.TraceScreen("ALIVE")
			if bNPCSpoke == false then
				-- Hydra.TraceScreen("TALK")
				Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_CALLOUT, idMonster)
				bNPCSpoke = true
			
			end
			
			if Hydra.ActorGetMonsterFamily(idMonster) == "knight" then
				--Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(idMonster, S_ANIM_KNEELING_IDLE,S_ANIM_KNEELING_STANDUP)
				Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(idMonster)
				Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, true)
			end
		end
	end
end

unk_993f312.value:
ID_FIREPIT = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "FIREPIT")[1]

T_MONSTERS = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "MONSTERS")

if Hydra.ActorGetMonsterFamily(T_MONSTERS[1]) == "knight" then
-- Initial Knight Setup
	for i, idGroup01 in ipairs(tStartingGroup01) do
		Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(idGroup01, S_ANIMSET_ENEMY_RANGED)
		UF_SittingAnims(idGroup01,S_ENEMY_RANGED_SIT_KNEES, S_ENEMY_RANGED_SIT_CROSS)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idGroup01, false)
	end

	for i, idGroup02 in ipairs(tStartingGroup02) do
		Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(idGroup02, S_ANIMSET_ENEMY_MELEE)
		UF_SittingAnims(idGroup02,S_ENEMY_MELEE_SIT_KNEES, S_ENEMY_MELEE_SIT_CROSS)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idGroup02, false)
	end
else
-- Initial Bandit Setup
	for i, idMonster in ipairs(T_MONSTERS) do
		--Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, false)
		
		SNO_JOB_STATE_AI_STATE = Hydra.ReferenceAIState("GenericJobState");
		Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(Hydra.QuestGetOwner(), SNO_JOB_STATE_AI_STATE, idMonster, 0.0);
	end
end
